title: prismAId - Open Science AI Tools for Systematic, Protocol-Based Literature Reviews
message: >-
  v0.10.1 - Updated dependencies and expanded LLM & OCR support.
  Updated alembica to v0.1.1 with breaking changes (migrated to official OpenAI SDK).
  Added support for Perplexity AI provider and new models: OpenAI GPT-5 series,
  Anthropic Claude 4.5 series, Google AI Gemini 2.5/3 series, Cohere Command A Reasoning.
  Added Apache Tika OCR fallback support for converting scanned PDFs and image-based documents
  with automatic fallback when standard conversion methods fail or return empty text.
  Updated CI/CD to use macOS 15 runners.
